The `storm.kafka.KafkaUtils` class invoked `calculatePartitionsForTask` method. And
the `GlobalPartitionInformation` class belongs to the package `storm.kafka.trident`,which aims to find  kafka partition informations.The `ISpoutPartition` interface,belongs to the package `storm.trident.spout`, was invoked by `GlobalPartitionInformation.getOrderedPartitions` method.

